productos.informacion: A silky, second-skin liquid highlighter that creates an instantly dewy, buildable glow while also nourishing skin so it looks on the bright side all day.
An innovative lip jelly that transforms into a lightweight oil, starting off glossy, then leaving lips tinted while staying comfortable—never sticky—all day.
A breakthrough bronzing stick that creates an instant sun-kissed glow and blends seamlessly for a second-skin finish—just swipe on, blend, and go!
A weightless, long-lasting liquid blush that blends and builds beautifully for a soft, healthy flush. Available in both matte and dewy finishes.
